    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cultural Context"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公布 reflects Chinese governance principles emphasizing official transparency and proper procedure.\nThe concept embodies the importance of formal channels for information dissemination and the\ncultural value placed on official authority in communication. Making something 公布 gives it\nlegitimacy and credibility in Chinese society."}],"type":"paragraph"}
